tips.text: My kids love the chicken sausages and often have great wine specials.
Ask for your Eye fillet on the bone - blue.

Was morning stop but alas I'm tired of wkly occurrences of forgetting my order, waiting 20+ mins for coffee; I'll miss their panini but not their prices... off to Richmond Rd Cafe I go. Mayor no more.
Janken delivers inspirational food, delicious fresh flavours with vibrant colours that leave your taste buds wanting more.
Lunchtime kebabs are $10 - chicken, lamb or felafel. Very nice!
The breakfasts were uniformly great, but it's picking a 'take home' treat that really makes the visit special.
Take a look upstairs for tge secret room where you can also book for private parties for free - sits up to 25 people! Perfect.
You can customise your own wraps. I have the vegetarian wrap with chicken. Soooo good!
